---
// ヒーローセクションコンポーネント
---

<section class="hero-section">
  <!-- コンテンツ -->
  <div class="relative z-20 container-custom py-8 px-8 h-full flex items-center justify-end">
          <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center w-full">
        <!-- 左側：テキストコンテンツ -->
        <div class="space-y-8 text-white ml-13">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
            SNSで新たな発見を。貴社のサービスや魅力を、届けるべき人に届けます。
          </p>
          
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
            次世代広告"SNS"で、<br />
            貴社に影響力を。
          </h1>
          
          <div class="bg-white text-blue-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block font-bold text-lg">
            日本全国｜TikTok運用代行ならBuzzLiminal
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-start">
          <button class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold text-xl px-12 py-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-200 flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">💬</span>
            <span>LINE相談はこちら</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 右側：スマホ画像 -->
      <div class="relative flex justify-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- スマホの画像はここに実際の画像を配置 -->
          <div class="w-64 h-96 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-2xl p-4 transform rotate-12">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-black rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-white text-6xl">📱</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 装飾要素 -->
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full opacity-30 animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 w-16 h-16 bg-pink-400 rounded-full opacity-30 animate-pulse delay-1000"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 背景装飾 -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-200 rounded-full opacity-10 -translate-y-48 translate-x-48 z-5"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-indigo-200 rounded-full opacity-10 translate-y-32 -translate-x-32 z-5"></div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    position: relative;
    background-image: url('/scramble.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    height: 570px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.7); /* 青いオーバーレイ（濃く） */
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-section > * {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }
</style>